Global Environmental Noise Monitoring System Market Insights
Environmental Noise Monitoring System Market size was valued at USD 3.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 5.9 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Environmental Noise Monitoring System Market Overview
The global Environmental Noise Monitoring System market was valued at approximately USD 1.2 billion in 2024, with expectations to reach USD 2.3 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 10.8% during the forecast period. The market is driven by rising concerns over noise pollution and stringent government regulations related to noise monitoring. Technological advancements, including the integration of real-time data analytics and IoT-enabled sensors, are further contributing to market growth. The increasing demand for noise pollution control in urban areas and industrial zones is also fostering the market expansion.

